Hi Guys, today I will present you our new multigame map :)
I spent a lot of work in it and hope you will enjoy.
At the start of each round, the players have to reach the end of a little course (takes 10seconds to reach or so). The fastest player can choose music and the minigame.
_____________________________________________________________________________
**First of all the Minigames:**

- Knife Battle:
A little Arena with a small path in middle of two platforms. In the middle of the path is a circle, when you jump through you can get one of 4 nades. But you will fall down and need to use a ladder to climb up again.

- Slide Fight:
You will slide down a little track and fight while you slide. On the track are some platforms, where you can find weapons and nades. After you reach the track the first time you gain a glock.

- Jump Race:
trampolines are fun right :)?
Winner is the first one climbed up the track with the help of trampolines.
With these trampolines you can win height. A how to use it description is in the minigame.

- Bhop:
My Bhop track is very hard!
But makes fun too :)

- Speed Shotgun:
A circle where you get pushed through, with a shotgun in the hand.
Very hard to hit more faster targets.
On the top of the middle pyramid is an awp.

- Capture the Flag:
First of all here a BIG THANKS to tophattwaffle for the great Idea.
you can visit him at www.tophattwaffle.com/?
Simple 2 Flags, in each base one, your team have to capture the enemy flag.
You only can capture the enemy flag, when your own flag is in base.
WITH RESPAWN :D

- Knife Duell Arena:
In this Arena is only 1on1. The fastest passed the random opened of four doors can fight against his enemy. In this arena is a little life regeneration.

- Survival Chaos (Minecraft Style):
At the start there will be 4 platforms and 4 bridges. In the middle of this is an enchanting table. This Table will shoot out some Minecraft things (for example Creepers or Crafting tables) for getting the platforms and bridges to fall down. The survivors on it have to dodge these things and try to survive.
After timeleft everyone gets an AWP to finish it.

- AIM Deagle (only Headshot):
I don´t have to say something or? :D

- Soccer:
Get the ball in the enemy gate to win.
If your team has won, you get AWP in a upper room, behind you is a little hole to teleport back to the socceryard.

- Physic Battle:
There are 13 Blocks (named to the dream Team)
Try to kill with these blocks your enemys. In the middle is a little trampoline.

- Pokémon nade Arena:
You have to hit 6 holes with nades for some special abilitys. Seems easy? You fight against the other teams for the holes. Both teams can´t get the same ability. After one Minute the fight will begin and you can buy weapons in the arena.

- Speedjumps:
Reach as first the end to win.

- TNT back and forth:
6 balls to go.
Try to kill the enemy team with the TNT Ball.
It will explode randomly between 15 and 30 seconds.
After 6 balls played and still no winner you can walk in the middle and knife it out.

- Zombie Survival:
Zombie Team have to kill the humans, Survivors have to survive 3Minutes.
Zombies HAVE REPSAWN!
Both Teams can be Zombie or Survivor.
It works fully without an Zombie Plugin.

_____________________________________________________________________________

Update v.2_2:

- fixed 1000hp bug in spawn area
- Knife Arena 1on1 got a new design
- TNT back and forth increased ball spawning, means more than 1 ball at time
- Physics in physic battle jumps now in the whole area
- changed music
- Zombie Arena Survivor glitch on the hills fixed
_____________________________________________________________________________

After 45Seconds the Player top didn´t choosed map it will be picked the knife Arena.

you should have a bhop plugin, for more fun :).


I hope for a lot of comments and ratings :)

A minigame i made with a little spare time.

Basically you try to climb to the top of the hill while avoiding the rolling balls.  They can be jumped but as they bounce it doesnt work always.
If you are hit by a ball you will be teleported to the jail where you will have to knife other ball victims.  If a ball just nicks you then you will recieve a small amount of damage rather than be teleported.  If you make it to the top of the hill then you can grab the awp that is up there, and have a clear view of the jail and can clean up the survivors, also you can shoot any of the other team that may still be trying to make it to the top, so being quick is important. 

i put the countdown at the start because some servers have freezetimes and its just a chance to get ready if you were not paying attention

it works well and i randomized the ball paths so it varies in difficulty every round, and there are no "safe" routes.

enjoy and tell me what you think.


Thanks to komaokc for his skybox.

MG DIVINE MULTIGAMES

A multigame map made by ProfessorOak & [SG] Paul with 15 levels to choose from! The multigame spawn/selection area has a bit of a twist to it compared to any generic multigame spawn with 5 random ways (3 climb, 1 hunt the creeper face and lava run) of 'getting chosen'. Before we go any further id like to thank ProfessorOak for letting me work on his map with him (which he originally started for his own multigame map), which progressed into this collaboration map that you are viewing right now, massive amount of respect to him.

MAP INFO

There are 15 levels that the 'winner' can select from by standing on the pressure pad in front of the level and then pressing 'e' on the map picture. The map has an auto picker setup for 60 seconds if nothing has been picked already. However although there are only 15 maps you will only be able to select 14 of them UNLESS YOU ARE RUNNING THE PLUGIN that comes in the .zip file. Thanks to kaemon who found this out, the music tracks in the map are optional for each client, the clients can totally mute the songs without the need to "snd_restart" mid game and lag for 1-2 seconds. They can go into Options -> Audio -> Music Volume, even if you turn this to off for the map you can still hear the game sounds. There are some unique level ideas in this map which we are proud to release such as the 2D race level (big thanks to kaemon for the entity setup and inspiration for the idea from his mg_2d_alpha map that he made like a year ago), 1hp containers is a pretty fun one, OaksWonderland, paulware (inspired by garryware) and more.

PLUGIN INFO - Server owners please read

This plugin is optional to have on your server, all that it does is handles one of the levels in the map. If its loaded it will unload the paulware stage button so that it can be selected. The plugin keeps track of players 'frags' and assigns the winner of the paulware stage with a weapon. The plugin also has a feature of !songlist too which will print the song name/artist/link to their console. The plugin is only loaded on the "mg_divine" prefix name and is not loaded once the map is not running. Thanks to Bob Loblaw for making the plugin, we have attached the .sp file along with the .smx if you would like to check the code before adding it to your server. If you are going to add the plugin I would also recommend setting the following in your server.cfg if you haven't already as there will be a REALLY SMALL chance of certain cvars being set once the map has changed, if the maps changed (rtv or admin force change) in the small window when the paulware map alters them. Here they are: - sv_friction 4 - sv_accelerate 5 - phys_timescale 1 Again id also like to thank ProfessorOak for giving me the opportunity to get back into mapping, he was the one who had already had 9 base levels before getting me involved. We think that the map is great fun to play on and we hope you guys enjoy it. Feedback is appreciated and thanks for downloading/reading if you have!

DeathRunner is a map, Inspired by Moozerker's Run Bitch Run. 
============================================================

**It consist of 21 CT and 2 T, both with different and fairly intriguing objective.**

![Gameplay](http://i.imgur.com/4z0Oj3M.png "Gameplay")

CT
==

CT, while having initial 150HP, has to avoid and dodge attacks from the T snipers and reach the finish line successfully. While doing so, CT has to overcome many different simple obstacles along their way. There are one checkpoints along the map in which they can regenerate their HP. In addition to this, there are several grenades and an AK-47 for distracting T (or perhaps killing them).

T
=

T simply has to kill all CT and prevent them from getting to the finished point. The choice of weapon that T is allowed to have is:

-  AWP
-  G3GS1
-  SG550

**Best played with more than 6 people, if there is less than 10 people, there should only be one Terrorist for fair gameplay.**

In this map there are 24 Counter-Terrorists slots and 1 Terrorist slot
The Terrorist starts in a small room. He must go through a teleporter and will be teleported to a cannon. If he does not go through the teleporter, he will die after 15 seconds. The Counter-Terrorists starts in one of four glassboxes. In each box fit 6 Counter-Terrorists. At the beginning of the round they get a knife.
If the Terrorist go through the teleporter, the four glassboxes will break.
Now the plate will start to rotate and the Terrorist try to kill the Counter-Terrorists with the cannon. He can shoot 5 sawblades successively with the left and the right cannon. After he shoot, he has to wait 2 second until he can shoot again. If you can shoot again, a green light will lights on, if not the light is red. The Counter-Terrorists try to survive 90 seconds.
